Interface ISongChangeObserver

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FileMenu, SaveLoadPanel

    public interface ISongChangeObserver
    Objects of this type can observe ISongChangers and will be notifyed if registerd in their observerlist. Used by the JComponents that are responsible for saving (makes export to XML possible).
